### 2.2.1 Traffic Accident Data

`read_csv()` of the **readr** package allows us to import csv files into R Studio.


::: {.cell}

```{.r .cell-code}
accidents <- read_csv("data/geospatial/thai_road_accident_2019_2022.csv")
```
:::

::: {.cell}

```{.r .cell-code}
glimpse(accidents)
```

::: {.cell-output .cell-output-stdout}
